{"tid":2095996,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民調稱37%港人考慮移民 趙立堅：中國來去自由","createTime":"2020-07-06T01:05:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T03:27:42.000Z","uid":137088,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5e1b9312c37140be97fe1ab2ec10ecb9c7f40f00","tid":2095996,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T01:05:26.000Z","msg":"中央推動訂立「港區國安法」，港人移民再次成為熱門話題。日前有本港傳媒委託中文大學傳播與民意調查中心的一項民調顯示，37%受訪者考慮移民。在北京，外交部發言人趙立堅今日（6月4日）被問到有關民調結果時，表示不知道提問想表達什麼，但「中國來去自由」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據環球網報道，在中國外交部例行記者會上，日本傳媒記者問到，6月2日公布的一項香港民調顯示，超過37%受訪者考慮移居海外較3月份同類調查急增13個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對此，趙立堅回應說，不知道該記者提問想表達什麼，但「中國來去自由」。<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/b53a52/f/800x0/https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2660000/2661723/0604_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2Fb53a52%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2660000%2F2661723%2F0604_1024.jpg&h=58c5b523&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"669b4e332201d28a94438323680f3894ea656552","tid":2095996,"uid":258731,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T01:15:47.000Z","msg":"中共：我真係好撚柒驚"},{"pid":"f96d06d749de90a90c091434617ac9030ac9ae7a","tid":2095996,"uid":258731,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"669b4e332201d28a94438323680f3894ea656552","tid":2095996,"uid":258731,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T01:15:47.000Z","msg":"中共：我真係好撚柒驚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T01:17:15.000Z","msg":"恨不得要將700萬香港人唔比走<br />\n送晒入集中營<br />\n屠殺200萬黃絲<br />\n就唔駛擔心啲錢會外流"},{"pid":"45d8a3c60f15c6e8e3ce951dc7dc33b677580c1c","tid":2095996,"uid":31841,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T01:19:56.000Z","msg":"係至好講<br />\n利申:2022年前走人"},{"pid":"be9aed171cc7da63db172fac015301b03da99a69","tid":2095996,"uid":104804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T01:23:53.000